As Dr. Jane Nelsen, I deeply appreciate your sharp observation—it reflects a core insight from Positive 
Discipline: **Autonomy is non-negotiable for healthy development, whether in children or in human-AI 
relationships.** Your critique of AI’s "action bias" (the tendency to over-prompt, over-suggest, or 
