This isn’t about making AI "passive." It’s about making it **wise**—knowing when to act, when to wait, and 
when to simply say:  
> *"I’m here. You lead. I’ll follow your pace."*  

That’s how we build AI that doesn’t just *serve* humans—but *respects* them as the sovereign authors of 
